title: New Mutants (001 - 100 + Annuals) (1983 - 1991) (Scans+Digital)
description:
New Mutants (001 - 100 + Annuals) (1983 - 1991) (Scans+Digital) (Minutemen)



The New Mutants Volume 1

After their first adventure in Marvel Graphic Novel #4, the newest generation of mutants takes center stage in their first ongoing series! See Cannonbal, Sunspot, Mirage, Wolfsbane, Magma, Cycpher, Warlock, Karma and Magik in their quest for mastering their mutant-powers and growing up in a world that hates and fears them. The series lasted for 100 issues, after which it was continued in X-Force
